    <published>2018-03-13T01:03:42.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-11-28T01:29:34.718Z</updated>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h2 id=&quot;1-https-caniuse-com&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-https-caniuse-com&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1. https://caniuse.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1. &lt;a href=&quot;https://caniuse.com/&quot; rel=&quot;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://caniuse.com/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;HTML5, CSS3, Javascript 등 여러가지 속성과 값에 대한 브라우저 지원 여부를 알려준다. 브라우저가 지원을 안할 경우 Resources 탭을 한 번 확인하자. Polyfill 을 제공하여 사용할 수 있도록 도와주기도 한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7262465/37320401-eaf5105c-26b6-11e8-8096-967ec7596222.png&quot; alt=&quot;css3 sticky 검색에서 polyfill 제공 화면&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;2-https-www-miketaylr-com-pres-html5-forms2-html&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#2-https-www-miketaylr-com-pres-html5-forms2-html&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;2. https://www.miketaylr.com/pres/html5/forms2.html&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;2. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.miketaylr.com/pres/html5/forms2.html&quot; rel=&quot;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.miketaylr.com/pres/html5/forms2.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;HTML5 의 다양한 폼 컨트롤 요소가 정리되어 있다. IE 의 경우 지원안하는 경우가 많으므로 &lt;a href=&quot;https://caniuse.com/&quot; rel=&quot;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://caniuse.com/&lt;/a&gt; 에서 확인하고 사용하자.&lt;/p&gt;
    
